WEBVTT

00:00.923 --> 00:01.802
Dear Henry.

00:03.173 --> 00:08.572
From the first moment I saw you, I knew I would never be the same.

00:09.257 --> 00:13.480
When you were born, I was born.

00:14.471 --> 00:16.217
Because you made me a mom.

00:16.575 --> 00:19.373
And as you grew, I also grew...

00:19.801 --> 00:24.457
...to be as good as possible for you forever.

00:24.943 --> 00:26.503
Love, Mom.

00:27.091 --> 00:29.827
Happy Mother's Day from Pampers.

